373
00:24:02,623 --> 00:24:06,708
[SPEAKER_26]: And here's the issue, because I've obviously reflected on this, because it's such a scandal.

374
00:24:08,230 --> 00:24:16,120
[SPEAKER_26]: What I've come to the conclusion is our system of government, whether you're a minister or you're in the courts, it depends on people telling the truth.

375
00:24:16,861 --> 00:24:20,245
[SPEAKER_26]: And in a number of scandals, the contaminated blood scandal,

376
00:24:20,292 --> 00:24:22,535
[SPEAKER_26]: The Hillsborough scandal, the Horizon scandal.

377
00:24:22,776 --> 00:24:26,221
