00:25:30,027 --> 00:25:31,890
[SPEAKER_26]: Man further back in the blue shirt.

389
00:25:32,772 --> 00:25:41,447
[SPEAKER_21]: Should Paula Vennells face criminal proceedings as a result of the bonuses she's profited on the back of the Postmasters?

390
00:25:41,967 --> 00:25:52,409
